title: Bim (Roy Forbes)
description:
Bim (Roy Forbes) is a folk singer songwriter from British Columbia, Canada known for his high soulful voice, bluesy rhythms and percussive guitar playing. He has opened for Supertramp and Santana and headlined most of Canada&#039;s major folk music festivals. His I&#039;m So Lonesome I Could Cry is the best cover ever, and his debut album Kid Full of Dreams is my desert island album.
